NCL MembershipSusan Welcome to NCL We will be beginning our membership drive with a social on Thursday January th The location is TBD A philanthropy event will follow at a later date An evite will be sent to all new members Dues for the year will be paid at that event Dues are payable to NCL Juniors You will also receive your membership packet Your sponsor Sarah Berry Cosponsor Lisa Thielemann If you have any questions please let me know Thanks Courtney Votaw VP Membership Do You Yahoo Send FREE video emails in Yahoo Mail videomail
